data.name: TextBox.Text
data.value:
SpawnProcessHidden is the same as SpawnProcess, except when launched, such as from Task Scheduler, no window appears, and the launched process is also hidden.
SpawnProcessHidden.exe -path "C:\Path\To\Process.exe" -args "-arg1 goesHere -arg2 goesHere" -workingdirectory "C:\Path\To"
-args and -workingdirectory are optional
If SpawnProcessHidden launched the process successfully, it will not show anything in the console. If there is an error, a window like this will pop up with the error message.
